results.title: Frankenstein (1973) #1
results.description: Mary Shelley’s classic, resurrected in the mighty Marvel manner! The most spine-tingling read in English literature, Frankenstein tells the tale of the monstrosity in man and man's creation. In the Arctic wild, explorer Robert Walton IV uncovers the body of a creature too nightmarish for words. Behold, the monster of Victor Frankenstein!
